<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.9.7">
<l>cenne larici ciṟupa ruppuc</l>
<l rend="indent">ceytavak kāram naṟuney pālāl</l>
<l>paṉṉiraṇ ṭutiru vōṇa maṭṭēṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">paṇṭu mippiḷḷai parica ṟivaṉ</l>
<l>iṉṉamu kappaṉnā ṉeṉṟu colli</l>
<l rend="indent">yellām viḻuṅkiṭ ṭuppōntu niṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>uṉmakaṉ taṉṉai yacōtai naṅkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">kūvik koḷḷā yivaiyum cilavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I prepared sugary treats made of red paddy rice</l>
<l rend="indent">and green gram, along with fragrant ghee and milk</l>
<l>for the twelve [days] of the holy Ōṇam [festival].</l>
<l>[But] I have known the nature of this child a long time.</l>
<l>He went about devouring everything,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying “I want more than this.”</l>
<l>My Lady, Yaśodā! Call your son to yourself.</l>
<l>These are only a few [of the things he’s done].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
